_sText:
This is my second map after zm_newcastle. I put more effort and time into this map. This map is based in a small town in the middle of nowhere. Enjoy!

Somebody had stated there were a lot of vending machines. Well theres a story behind why. This little town has no running water, which is why all the machined vend water, and why the toilets still have poo in them.

I didn't make this final since I am considering making it a little larger. 


Changes from v3
* Added env_cubemaps to get rid of that 
   nasty green glare on weapons
* Removed playerclip from above fence and added 
   rock texture to improve realism  
* Added a doorway in an "impossible" room outside.
* Widened doorway "                                            "
* Changed sky model
* Made it more awesome
